TY  - JOUR
TI  - An Information Good Market with Symmetric Externalities
AU  - Muto, Shigeo
AB  - [In this paper, we study a monopolistic market for an information good possessing external effects, and investigate how far the information good is diffused from its owner to demanders through trades.]
